{"tid":158135,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連環巴士「鎅褲黨」落網　兩中國匪身藏11鎅刀","createTime":"2017-03-16T05:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T06:13:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcadd7f4b9a34ef6367a569fb3f90487d6d3271c","tid":158135,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"警方本周二破獲一個活躍西九龍區的「鎅褲黨」，拘捕兩名正在九巴268X上犯案的內地匪徒，身懷7100元現金的事主幸保不失，但牛仔褲及銀包已在不知情下被「劏開」，其中一匪身上被搜出11塊鋒利刀片。 <br />\n<br />\n被捕兩名男子分別姓賀及姓曹，同為43歲，已被落案控以一項盜竊罪，今日（16日）在西九龍裁判法院應訊。據悉兩人為湖南籍，數日前持雙程證來港，其中曹有多次來港紀錄，涉嫌與今年1月至3月初九龍城、旺角、深水埗及黃大仙發生的巴士鎅褲盜竊案有關，案中受害人合共損失約1.2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n近期全港多區接連發生巴士鎅褲盜竊案，西九龍為重災區，更有蔓延至港島情況；日前就有網友在facebook專頁上載帖文指，在北角搭巴士時遇上鎅褲黨，幸及時警覺，未有財物損失，並展示聲稱被鎅破褲袋及銀包的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，西九龍總區情報組鑑於區內近日接連發生鎅褲盜竊案，相信有黨匪活躍犯案，遂加強巡邏。本周二下午1時許，數名探員在油麻地近眾坊街附近巴士站巡邏時，發現兩名可疑男子隨市民登上一輛268X九巴，探員尾隨上車及監視，發現兩人到上層分別坐在57歲姓鍾男乘客旁邊及前方座位。其間，探員見坐在鍾身旁的疑人暗中用刀片鎅穿其牛仔褲右後袋及偷去銀包，但鍾全不知情。<br />\n<br />\n探員見時機成熟，即採取行動，兩名男子見事敗企圖反抗逃走，迅即被制服及起回贓物，鍾才驚覺牛仔褲袋及銀包被鎅破，銀包內7100元現金得保不失。<br />\n<br />\n探員在其中一人身上檢獲11塊疑用作犯案刀片，不排除兩人涉及近期多宗同類案件，將他們帶署調查，案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊第10隊跟進。警方呼籲市民提防扒手，在公共交通工具上時刻小心保管手袋、銀包和手提電話等財物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170316/s00001/1489595257317\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170316%2Fs00001%2F1489595257317&h=5de834bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a25b6cad17c5237d13cda6217518fa388c76067","tid":158135,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/16c80001b1c084c25d60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2F16c80001b1c084c25d60&h=f7a501ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11621dc032a1e436b8008305345a91144f25cf77","tid":158135,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170316/s00001/1489595257317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170316%2Fs00001%2F1489595257317&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=f3dba67c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170316%2Fs00001%2F1489595257317&h=00dd59e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170316/s00001/1489595257317</a>"},{"pid":"cbf762689e240cc5fba2f4ca6e87c36f9233eab0","tid":158135,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"專才系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78d7cec0ad9cefc93ab6ba040112f7f2dc31fa0","tid":158135,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/16c80001b1c084c25d60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2F16c80001b1c084c25d60&h=f7a501ef&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n洞庭湖草頭鄉上陽村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你呢"},{"pid":"704882af92f4278bebe5d07ff741022f246445ba","tid":158135,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T05:22:12.000Z","msg":"要不是警察保護市民，香港人早就完蛋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1468df08b887ca8cb3ab8b8946cf884fa7380ec2","tid":158135,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/16c80001b1c084c25d60\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2F16c80001b1c084c25d60&h=f7a501ef&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n小李飛（𠝹）刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}